function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	local followerNeyrelle = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Neyrelle_Follower_Magic")
	local followerLorath = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Lorath_Follower")
	
	Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerNeyrelle)
	Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerLorath)
	
	-- Neyrelle move action
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerNeyrelle, false)
	Hydra.QActorSheath(followerNeyrelle)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerNeyrelle, idNeyrelleDoor, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerNeyrelle, idNeyrelleDoor)
	
	-- Lorath move action
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerLorath, false)
	Hydra.QActorSheath(followerLorath)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerLorath, idLorathDoor, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerLorath, idLorathDoor)
	
	-- Wait for both to be done
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerLorath)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(followerLorath, 0.5)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerNeyrelle)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(followerNeyrelle, 0.5)

end
